      "body": "# IOHK Checkpointing Presentation and Q&A\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Checkpointing Presentation\r\n\r\nIOHK (IOG) has released ECIP-1097 #347 which covers their proposed \"Checkpointing\" system which aims to prevent 51% attacks on ETC. They'll explain the proposal and conduct a presentation, followed by a community Q&A.\r\n\r\nThe goal of this call is simply to get contributors, community members, stakeholders and especially other teams who have created similar proposals (@max-sanchez, @Dexaran, to properly understand this proposal. More details to come.\r\n\r\n- When: Date/Time TBD; 30 minute presentation followed by Q&A\r\n\r\n- Where: ETC Discord https://discord.gg/bGtG4PY #Presentation Calls channel. (Be advised: When joining the ETC Discord there is a 10 minute wait before one can join the server) or possibly Crowdcast.\r\n\r\n## Q&A\r\n\r\nQuestions will be submitted via https://www.sli.do/ (Slido meeting code will be posted when date/time is confirmed)\r\n\r\n## References\r\n\r\n- Checkpointing Explanation Video: https://youtu.be/aasUIB1W81E\r\n- Securing Ethereum Classic via Checkpointing:  https://youtu.be/1JeL4pAjmXM \r\n- Securing PoW Ledgers via Checkpointing Paper: https://iohk.io/en/research/library/papers/securing-proof-of-work-ledgers-via-checkpointing/\r\n",
